trans-unit.source: The ViewService class maps visuals to underlying model items.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ViewService tilordner visuelle effekter til underliggende modellelementer.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Services.ModelService> and ViewService classes are required for the designer to function.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Services.ModelService>og ViewService klasser kreves for designer til funksjonen.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Services.ModelService>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Activities.Design.View.DesignerView> class, which is responsible for processing user input and routing it to commands, requires both of these services to map user input back to the model.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Activities.Design.View.DesignerView>klassen som er ansvarlig for å behandle brukerinndata og distribuere den til kommandoer, krever at begge disse tjenestene ikke tilordne brukerinndata tilbake til modellen.</xref:System.Activities.Design.View.DesignerView>

trans-unit.source: Returns the model corresponding to the view, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if there is no model that matches the view.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer modellen tilsvarer visningen, eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> om det finnes ingen modell som samsvarer med visningen.

trans-unit.source: The view object that you want to find the model for.
trans-unit.target: Visningsobjekt som du ønsker å finne modellen for.

trans-unit.source: Returns the corresponding model as a <xref:System.Activities.Design.Model.ModelItem>, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if there is no model for the given view object.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer den tilsvarende modellen som en <xref:System.Activities.Design.Model.ModelItem>, eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> Hvis det finnes ingen modell for det angitte objektet.</xref:System.Activities.Design.Model.ModelItem>

trans-unit.source: Returns the view corresponding to the given model, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if there is no view for the model.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer visningen tilsvarer den angitte modellen eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> Hvis det er ingen visning for modellen.

trans-unit.source: The model to return the view object for.
trans-unit.target: Modell til å returnere visningsobjekt for.

trans-unit.source: Returns the view for this model as a <xref href="System.Windows.DependencyObject"></xref>, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if there is no view.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer visningen for denne modellen som en <xref href="System.Windows.DependencyObject"> </xref>, eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> Hvis det er ingen visning.

trans-unit.source: model does not represent a valid model for this service.
trans-unit.target: modelrepresenterer ikke en gyldig modell for denne tjenesten.
